using graphics lib
	the-Window : a simple window

	repeat
		Shape : a square
		Shape's Colour   : random colour
		Shape's Position : random point
		Shape's Size     : random from 10 to 100
		Shape's Heading  : random from 1 to 90
		add Shape to the-Window
	… 100 times

	Turn : 2
	Degree : 0
	animate 60 ticks per second
		for each Shape in (the-Window's Shapes) do
			change Shape heading by Turn degrees
		update the-Window
		Degree : Degree + Turn
	… until [Degree ≥ 360]

"Finished" ↲
